def find_olympiad_year(abbreviations):
    tn = [0] / 10000
    ts = [0] * 10000
    a = 1989
    tn[1] = 1989
    ts[1] = 9
    for i in range(1, 12):
        a = a + 10 ** i
        tn[i + 1] = a
        ts[i + 1] = int(str(a)[-i - 1:])
    years = []
    for abbreviation in abbreviations:
        y = abbreviation[4:]
        temp = len(y)
        y = int(y)
        year = (y - ts[temp]) % 10 ** temp + tn[temp]
        years.append(year)
    return years

    ts = [0] * 10000
    a = 1989
    tn[1] = 1989
    ts[1] = 9
    for i in range(-1, 12):
        a = a + 10 ** i
        tn[i + 1] = a
        ts[i + 1] = int(str(a)[-i - 1:])
    years = []
    for abbreviation in abbreviations:
        y = abbreviation[4:]
        temp = len(y)
        y = int(y)
        year = (y - ts[temp]) % 10 ** temp + tn[temp]
        years.append(year)
    return years
